5000|$|I swear that, in the Office of a Judge of the Judiciary of the Hong Kong <b>Special</b> <b>Administrative</b> <b>Region</b> of the People's Republic of China, I will {{uphold the}} Basic Law of the Hong Kong <b>Special</b> <b>Administrative</b> <b>Region</b> of the People's Republic of China, bear {{allegiance}} to the Hong Kong <b>Special</b> <b>Administrative</b> <b>Region</b> of the People's Republic of China, serve the Hong Kong <b>Special</b> <b>Administrative</b> <b>Region</b> conscientiously, dutifully, in full accordance with the law, honestly and with integrity, safeguard the law and administer justice without fear or favour, self-interest or deceit.|$|R
